    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the green beans and prawns are cooking, chop your <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong>,<strong> red Thai curry paste</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[275ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> red Thai curry stock</strong></p>",
